37424>>>    // not set the Server property or send ADDOStructure. We will simply use
37424>>>    // DDO's to mine data and generate HTML for our cWebHTMLBox objects.
37424>>>    // It is the HTML in these objects that is sent to the client each time 
37424>>>    // this page is shown.
